item.title: Confused Need help
item.dc:creator: @Fireweaver0 Fireweaver0
item.description:
@Fireweaver0 wrote:

You need to fix your Path in Environment Variables.
Go back to your environment variables and under SYSTEM variables make sure your Path value is this

C:\WINDOWS\system32

Then do the ipconfig/all again.

P.S.
When you do your Variables you are only supposed to edit you USER variables not SYSTEM.

Read full topic
